# Vite

## install

### npm 

```shell
npm install -D vite
```

### yarn

```shell
yarn add -D vite
```



## usage

### npm

```shell
npx vite
npx vite build
```

### yarn

```shell
yarn vite
yarn vite build
```

> vite 不仅可以打包，自带HMR功能

